   <narrative xml:lang="EN">DONATE SOLAR LIGHT TO 5000CHILDREN IN RURAL UGANDA</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Pearl Entrepreneurs Academy (PEA) is a charitable Community Based Organization based in Mayuge Uganda founded by the young people to give back to the community.At night, for lighting, they have no choice but to use kerosene lanterns and open flame candles. The smoke from these lights sources is hazardous to their health. The flames are also a fire hazard. PEA is helping to address these issues by providing safe, renewable, solar-powered lights to kids and students read, study and do school work</narrative>
  </description>
